timing_enable...h_clock_gating(25.10)    timing_enable...h_clock_gating(25.10)

Name
       timing_enable_data_through_clock_gating

Syntax
       timing_enable_data_through_clock_gating

       {true | false}

       Default: true

       When  set to false, blocks signals arriving on the enable of the clock-
       gating check.

       When set to true, allows both data and clock signals at the enable  pin
       of a clock-gating check to propagate forward past the check.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

